snippet.title: Why Amber so scare stand look-What happend monkey Amber
snippet.description:
Hello everyone! 

In this video is more focus on baby Amber playing with other smaller monkey. We all knew that baby Amber receive less little love and care from his mother since he was a baby. His mother is loving his big brother than him, he wants his mom to love his as she love his brother but he rarely get. 

Baby Amber leave his mother and go to find the food very often because his mother did not feed him well and sometimes he only can eat the remain food from his brother. So the best way to survive is to truth himself and become independence. 

Right now baby Amber is play so happy like crazy with other baby monkey Bridget, Rain, Rojoel and Pipper all are his best friends. 

6:40 while playing, Amber heard the noise from other distance of dog attack, he is standing and looking around then begin to play again as the battle is finished. 

9:12 Romeo just arrived .. Romeo is one of the monkey free and easy monkey in this tribe, he does not care so much with other monkey, she like to stay alone, play alone and rarely play with other monkey except taking care his brother - Daniel. 

Thank you very much for watching, please like, comment and share our video ...

Cheer - Kitty Monkey
